name: Strike Force Origami
description:
Take control of an ORIGAMI fighter drone!

This paper airplane is armed with machine guns, forward firing rockets and guided missiles!  

Dodge enemy planes and missiles. Avoid flying into buildings and pylons. Pick-up various power-ups. Call in your wingmen and dominate the orange skies! 

--REQUIREMENTS--
This game was created for use with Android Phones with Multi-core processors.
Entry Level Android phones may experience sluggish game play.

--GAME ENGINE--
This Game was created using BUILDBOX 3.
BUILDBOX 3 is an amazing game engine that allows just about anyone to create games without writing a single line of code!

GET BUILDBOX 3 and start creating your own games!
